  "lyrics": "Ha ha fuck well, I guess that's too loud wait You never run and you know now you hear it get a level when you hear it in the show And you know you just jumpin' man where do you go? Mario, Chico, got the wall whistle come on Woo woo woo got the wall whistle come on Take your mind in different flows, take your line in different no's It's just the way we go, it's just the thing we do Stomp my horn and I'm bound to you Can you hear it? It's something new I got up, down, Chico, motherfuckin' no Up, down, Chico, everywhere I go Shit's been forever, it's a story I'm trying to get it heavier than your mind, ay Now I know, that you, fucking disappear Now I know, that you, fuck you, disappear Take away the darkness, take away the darkness Have my heart be a spark for all the hotness Have the hotness, have the ladies Watch them come in, buy a Mercedes Every time I blow, I know you know That it's just me, homie Don't get jealous of the other bitches, ay Come with me around, to save my trip, ay Up, down, Chico, every time that I look Up, down, Chico, with every rhyme that I book Inside your mind, inside your heart Don't you just see, I'm wearing stars, ay",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 5.380000114440918,
      "text": "Ha ha fuck well, I guess that's too loud wait",
      "start": 1.399999976158142
    },
    {
      "end": 34.79999923706055,
      "text": "You never run and you know now you hear it get a level when you hear it in the show",
      "start": 30
    },
    {
      "end": 38.220001220703125,
      "text": "And you know you just jumpin' man where do you go?",
      "start": 34.79999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 41.720001220703125,
      "text": "Mario, Chico, got the wall whistle come on",
      "start": 38.47999954223633
    },
    {
      "end": 44.34000015258789,
      "text": "Woo woo woo got the wall whistle come on",
      "start": 41.720001220703125
    },
    {
      "end": 48.040000915527344,
      "text": "Take your mind in different flows, take your line in different no's",
      "start": 44.5
    },
    {
      "end": 51.279998779296875,
      "text": "It's just the way we go, it's just the thing we do",
      "start": 48.040000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 54.36000061035156,
      "text": "Stomp my horn and I'm bound to you",
      "start": 51.29999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 56.939998626708984,
      "text": "Can you hear it? It's something new",
      "start": 54.5
    },
    {
      "end": 60.459999084472656,
      "text": "I got up, down, Chico, motherfuckin' no",
      "start": 56.939998626708984
    },
    {
      "end": 63.779998779296875,
      "text": "Up, down, Chico, everywhere I go",
      "start": 60.459999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 66.80000305175781,
      "text": "Shit's been forever, it's a story",
      "start": 63.779998779296875
    },
    {
      "end": 70.41999816894531,
      "text": "I'm trying to get it heavier than your mind, ay",
      "start": 66.80000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 76.5199966430664,
      "text": "Now I know, that you, fucking disappear",
      "start": 70.95999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 82.87999725341797,
      "text": "Now I know, that you, fuck you, disappear",
      "start": 76.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 86.33999633789062,
      "text": "Take away the darkness, take away the darkness",
      "start": 82.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 89.68000030517578,
      "text": "Have my heart be a spark for all the hotness",
      "start": 86.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 92.76000213623047,
      "text": "Have the hotness, have the ladies",
      "start": 89.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 95.81999969482422,
      "text": "Watch them come in, buy a Mercedes",
      "start": 92.76000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 98.66000366210938,
      "text": "Every time I blow, I know you know",
      "start": 95.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 101.76000213623047,
      "text": "That it's just me, homie",
      "start": 98.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 105.18000030517578,
      "text": "Don't get jealous of the other bitches, ay",
      "start": 101.76000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 108.81999969482422,
      "text": "Come with me around, to save my trip, ay",
      "start": 105.18000030517578
    },
